`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Pmote
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * pmote <action>

 Pmote, similar to Emote, is used to express actions and emotions, but will
substitute a target's name for "you" and "your".  That is, if Alice sends the
command  pmote bonks Bob. then Bob will see  Alice bonks you. and everyone else
in the room will see  Alice bonks Bob. 

 See also Emote and Pose.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
